<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dream-v">dream <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /driːm/    美 /driːm/  </p>
<p>(dreamed / dreamt, dreamed / dreamt)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>做 (梦)；梦见；想象：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>dreamed a strange dream</strong> last night. 
我昨晚做了一个奇怪的梦。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>dreamed about</strong> you last night.
我昨晚梦见你了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>dreamed that</strong> I took part in a race.
我梦到自己参加了一场田径比赛。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>梦想：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have always <strong>dreamed of / about</strong> starting my own company.
我一直梦想自己创业。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I never <strong>dreamed</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) I’d actually get the job.
我从没想过会真的得到那份工作。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>dreamer /'driːmə(r)/ n   </p></div>